vote.description: Select which farms to allocate MELAI rewards to using your WNUBAI balance
vote.descriptionMainnet: Voting for Mainnet jar reward weights occurs on-chain. Your WNUBAI balance dictates how much power you have with regard to how the platform emissions are distributed. To vote, you must select at least one jar, then ensure the sum of your vote(s) equals 100%. If your vote is valid, you can cast your vote with the "Cast Mainnet Vote" button.
vote.descriptionOffchain: Voting for sidechain jar reward weights occurs offchain. Your WNUBAI balance dictates how much power you have with regard to how the platform emissions are distributed. Your chain vote is for the distribution of emissions among the many chain supported by Melon. Votes for specific jars or jar strategies will give those jars access to a portion of the emissions allocated to the chain in the former part of the vote. To vote, you must select at least one chain or chain strategy and one jar or jar strategy, then attribute a total of 100% of your vote in each of these categories. If your vote is valid, you can cast your vote with the "Cast Offchain Vote" button.
